    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless, displaying a deep, mirror-like shine with no scratches, chips, or dents of any kind. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, with the leather and trim appearing as though they just left the factory. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a comprehensive service history and zero outstanding issues, offering a true collector-quality experience for its next owner.",
