    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly vehicle that gets the job done? This car is in fair condition and has plenty of life left in it! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a dependable choice for anyone needing a functional daily driver at a great value.",
