    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has clearly been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior paint retains a strong shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and all features are fully operational, making this a dependable and attractive choice for its next owner.",
