    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the 'mint' standard. This car has been meticulously garaged and maintained with an obsessive attention to detail, resulting in an exterior finish that retains its deep, showroom-floor luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark in sight. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of perfection; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and entirely free of wear, complemented by the original factory scent. Every technological feature, from the advanced navigation system to the ambient lighting, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a whisper-quiet engine and a comprehensive, documented service history that confirms its pampered life. This is a rare opportunity to own a pre-owned vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
